38:53.914 --> 38:56.881
My question is tonight, will you be safe?

38:58.504 --> 38:59.346
Are you ready?

39:00.706 --> 39:18.254
We're talking about the destruction of everything that we see and know in this world, all of the things that we hold so precious, our homes, our cars, our businesses, our neighborhoods, all of our possessions, these things that have absorbed our time, our salaries, these things that we have called necessities.

39:18.514 --> 39:24.884
Honey, one day they will all be dissolved and what then will be left.

39:25.104 --> 39:28.690
Well, I'll tell you what to be left, the things that are not seen.

39:31.362 --> 39:38.192
things that are not seen, the important things, the spiritual things.

39:38.212 --> 39:44.000
Yeah, what you build up on this world is not going to do anything but turn and melt one of these days.

39:44.881 --> 39:57.500
What you do for the Father, what you do for the Kingdom, what you do for your Master and Savior Jesus Christ, that will survive all time.

39:57.520 --> 39:59.122
It's the only thing that's going to last.

39:59.298 --> 40:01.874
It's the only thing that's going to be left at the end of it all.

